        {
            "text": "While modes with large statistics can provide precise measurements of BFs and B ( * ) s properties, first observations of several CP -eigenstate B 0 s decays are a confirmation of the large potential of our 120 fb \u22121 e + e \u2212 \u2192 \u03a5(5S) data sample and advocate an ambitious B 0 s program at super-B factories.",
